\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3}{\ignorespaces Barron norm $C_{h^*_K}$ of the HAM residual as a function of truncation order $K$. The geometric decay with rate $\rho _{\mathrm  {Barron}} \approx 0.26$ matches the supremum-norm decay, verifying the spectral regularity condition assumed in Proposition~\ref {prop:HAM}.}}{11}{figure.3}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:barron}{{3}{11}{Barron norm $C_{h^*_K}$ of the HAM residual as a function of truncation order $K$. The geometric decay with rate $\rho _{\mathrm {Barron}} \approx 0.26$ matches the supremum-norm decay, verifying the spectral regularity condition assumed in Proposition~\ref {prop:HAM}}{figure.3}{}}
